@startuml
title Predictive Maintenance System - Deployment Sequence

actor "DevOps Engineer" as DevOps
participant "ocp_deploy.py" as DeployScript
participant "OpenShift CLI (oc)" as OC
participant "kubectl" as kubectl
participant "OpenShift Cluster" as OpenShift
participant "Strimzi Operator" as Strimzi
participant "Kafka Cluster" as Kafka
participant "MinIO Storage" as MinIO
participant "Seldon Core" as Seldon
participant "Docker Registry" as Registry
participant "Consumer App" as Consumer
participant "Producer App" as Producer

== Infrastructure Setup ==
DevOps -> OpenShift: Deploy Strimzi Kafka Operator
activate OpenShift
OpenShift -> Strimzi: Install Operator
activate Strimzi
Strimzi --> OpenShift: Operator Ready
deactivate Strimzi
OpenShift --> DevOps: Operator Installed
deactivate OpenShift

DevOps -> OC: Execute kafka.sh script
activate OC
OC -> OpenShift: Apply kafka.yaml manifest
activate OpenShift
OpenShift -> Strimzi: Create Kafka CR
activate Strimzi
Strimzi -> Kafka: Deploy Kafka Cluster
activate Kafka
Kafka --> Strimzi: Cluster Running
Strimzi --> OpenShift: Kafka Ready
deactivate Strimzi
OpenShift --> OC: Deployment Complete
deactivate OpenShift
OC --> DevOps: Kafka Deployed
deactivate OC

DevOps -> OC: Apply minio-full.yaml
activate OC
OC -> OpenShift: Deploy MinIO Resources
activate OpenShift
OpenShift -> MinIO: Create MinIO Instance
activate MinIO
MinIO --> OpenShift: Storage Ready
OpenShift --> OC: MinIO Deployed
deactivate OpenShift
OC --> DevOps: Object Storage Available
deactivate OC

== Model Training and Preparation ==
DevOps -> DeployScript: Execute ocp_deploy.py
activate DeployScript
DeployScript -> DeployScript: Read Predictor.py
DeployScript -> DeployScript: Prepare Dockerfile

DeployScript -> OC: Build Docker Image
activate OC
OC -> Registry: Push Model Image
activate Registry
Registry --> OC: Image Stored
deactivate Registry
OC --> DeployScript: Image Build Complete
deactivate OC

== Model Deployment ==
DeployScript -> kubectl: Apply Seldon-Deployment.yaml
activate kubectl
kubectl -> OpenShift: Create SeldonDeployment CR
activate OpenShift
OpenShift -> Seldon: Deploy Model Server
activate Seldon
Seldon -> Registry: Pull Model Image
activate Registry
Registry --> Seldon: Image Retrieved
deactivate Registry
Seldon -> Seldon: Initialize Predictor
Seldon -> Seldon: Expose REST API
Seldon --> OpenShift: Model Server Running
OpenShift --> kubectl: Deployment Created
deactivate OpenShift
kubectl --> DeployScript: Model Deployed
deactivate kubectl

DeployScript -> OC: Create OpenShift Route
activate OC
OC -> OpenShift: Expose Seldon Service
activate OpenShift
OpenShift --> OC: Route Created
deactivate OpenShift
OC --> DeployScript: Model API Exposed
deactivate OC
DeployScript --> DevOps: Deployment Complete
deactivate DeployScript

== Application Deployment ==
DevOps -> OC: Apply consumer-deployment.yaml
activate OC
OC -> OpenShift: Deploy Consumer Application
activate OpenShift
OpenShift -> Consumer: Create Consumer Pod
activate Consumer
Consumer -> Kafka: Subscribe to Image Topic
Consumer -> Seldon: Connect to Model API
Consumer -> MinIO: Configure Storage Access
Consumer --> OpenShift: Consumer Ready
OpenShift --> OC: Consumer Deployed
deactivate OpenShift
OC --> DevOps: Consumer Running
deactivate OC

DevOps -> OC: Deploy Producer Application
activate OC
OC -> OpenShift: Deploy Producer Resources
activate OpenShift
OpenShift -> Producer: Create Producer Pod
activate Producer
Producer -> Kafka: Connect to Topic
Producer --> OpenShift: Producer Ready
OpenShift --> OC: Producer Deployed
deactivate OpenShift
OC --> DevOps: Producer Running
deactivate OC

== Runtime Verification ==
DevOps -> Producer: Verify Webcam Connection
Producer --> DevOps: Image Capture Active

DevOps -> Kafka: Check Topic Status
Kafka --> DevOps: Topics Available

DevOps -> Consumer: Verify Processing
Consumer -> Kafka: Poll Messages
Kafka --> Consumer: Image Data
Consumer -> Seldon: POST /predict
activate Seldon
Seldon -> Seldon: Run Inference
Seldon --> Consumer: Prediction Results
deactivate Seldon
Consumer -> MinIO: Store Results
MinIO --> Consumer: Stored Successfully
deactivate MinIO
Consumer --> DevOps: Pipeline Operational

DevOps -> OpenShift: Deploy show_data.html
activate OpenShift
OpenShift --> DevOps: Visualization Available
deactivate OpenShift
deactivate Consumer
deactivate Producer
deactivate Kafka

@enduml
